Label: Country of manufacture (product part)
Description: An ONIX code identifying the country in which a product part was manufactured, if different product parts were manufactured in different countries. This information is needed in some countries to meet regulatory requirements. Optional and non-repeating.
Format: <dd>Fixed length, two letters, based on ISO 3166-1. Note that ISO 3166-1 specifies that country codes shall be sent as upper case only</dd>
